    {
      "id": 36,
      "section": {
        "id": 35,
        "title": "Recommendations",
        "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858",
        "updated": null,
        "parts": null
      },
      "type": {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "Paragraph",
        "feHandlerIndex": "Paragraph"
      },
      "displayText": "Recommendations from me:",
      "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
      "updated": null,
      "displayOrder": 1,
      "contents": [
        {
          "id": 37,
          "content": "Every recommendation you give, try to follow it yourself.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 1
        },
        {
          "id": 38,
          "content": "Make code more readable (Clean Code, DRY).",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 3
        },
        {
          "id": 39,
          "content": "Don't expect others to do something you wouldn't do yourself.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 5
        },
        {
          "id": 40,
          "content": "Before changing anything, try creating something new instead.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 6
        },
        {
          "id": 41,
          "content": "Gather suggestions and do something if they are to many.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 7
        },
        {
          "id": 42,
          "content": "If you'd like to change something, think twice — sometimes changing your mind about the problem is easier and better.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 8
        },
        {
          "id": 43,
          "content": "Don't take new tools until you've mastered the existing ones.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 10
        },
        {
          "id": 44,
          "content": "don't rush time, or time will break you down.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 11
        },
        {
          "id": 45,
          "content": "when you see something think how some one sees this in they're eyes.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 12
        },
        {
          "id": 46,
          "content": "don't solve imagined problems use imagination to create something new.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 13
        },
        {
          "id": 47,
          "content": "don't break something, before you make something to take it's place.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 14
        },
        {
          "id": 48,
          "content": "Use tools but doesn't allow tools to own you.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 15
        },
        {
          "id": 49,
          "content": "Run single direction a time",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 16
        },
        {
          "id": 50,
          "content": "The more turns you make the worth path you have chosen.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 17
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "section": {
        "id": 35,
        "title": "Recommendations",
        "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858",
        "updated": null,
        "parts": null
      },
      "type": {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "Paragraph",
        "feHandlerIndex": "Paragraph"
      },
      "displayText": "Recommendations related to dev:",
      "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
      "updated": null,
      "displayOrder": 2,
      "contents": [
        {
          "id": 51,
          "content": "SOLID — even if you can't fully apply it, aim for the closest option.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 1
        },
        {
          "id": 52,
          "content": "Try to follow KISS, but if it's impossible, keep it complex only when necessary.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 2
        },
        {
          "id": 53,
          "content": "YARGNI — use it always and you'll find some free time.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 3
        },
        {
          "id": 54,
          "content": "Clean Code doesn't make your code better, faster or simpler. It makes your code more readable!",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 4
        },
        {
          "id": 55,
          "content": "Humans should work with humans, not on creating code that no one understands!",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 5
        },
        {
          "id": 56,
          "content": "Don't take dogs leg and move forward, learn how properly to give command.",
          "created": "2026-03-09T09:39:25.318858Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 6
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}